resources.string: I was born in St. Petersburg, Russia and moved to Toronto when I was 5 years old. I write a style blog, am a contributor to Conde Nast\'s

Canadian platform Fashionation TV, Skype\'s Global Fashion Ambassador, and am also a full-time internationally represented model. I live every day with maximum positivity and strive to emit radiance, and I honestly have no idea where I'll be headed tomorrow, which makes life all the more fun.
